    ABOUT US

    OVER EASY KITCHEN

    OEK

    Over Easy Kitchen is a breakfast, brunch, and lunch restaurant with three locations in the heart of New Jersey including Marlboro, Holmdel, and Fair Haven. We are open seven days a week from 8am to 3pm. Our dedication to our customers and focus on providing excellent food, décor, and service has led to our success. We provide a unique blend of classic breakfast, brunch, and lunch dishes along with new and revolving weekend specials that you haven’t seen before. So stop by one of our locations to see what’s new!

    DINE WITH US

    YOUR CULINARY ADVENTURE AWAITS

    Whether you’re in the mood for a sweet breakfast or a savory lunch, OEK has got you covered. We put a twist on breakfast classics to make them unique and full of flavor in every bite. Some of our customers’ favorites include our Lemon Ricotta Pancakes and our Fancy Burrata. Our talented chefs make creative specials using fresh and seasonal ingredients every weekend. Be on the lookout for these delicious dishes that will be sure to impress you.
